reviewText: I thought this was harder than ATS #1 because you're dropping down to touch the floor for some of the moves and it's fast! It's almost like doing burpees at crack speed. However, even with modifications on my end, I still got a great workout.
What in the hell is this $***, and why was it allowed to be recorded and distributed nationally.
I have not finished this workout it is too hard for me but gives me something to look forward to
i really like this.  easy to learn and really a great workout.

lots of big jumping and rhythm to play
